{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4ea3b7ac0a","title":"给李淑一的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"10e902717d","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":11,"articleId":"4ea3b7ac0a"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji38","name":"毛泽东全集第38卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/38-OCR.pdf"},{"id":"wenji7","name":"毛泽东文集第七卷（1999）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"中央文献研究室","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives9/main/books/wenji7.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji38":{"comments":[{"id":"8d94599eea","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"4ea3b7ac0a","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"李淑一（1901—1997），湖南长沙人，柳直萄的夫人，当时是湖南长沙第十中学语文教员。"},{"id":"d3e07b588a","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"4ea3b7ac0a","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"开慧，即杨开慧（1901—1930），湖南长沙人，毛泽东的夫人。1921年加入中国共产党，1930年10月被国民党反动派速捕，11月晒牡。"},{"id":"7d5d96f41e","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"4ea3b7ac0a","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指《虞美人·枕上》（《毛泽东诗词集》，中央文献出版社1996年版，第166页）。"},{"id":"b20145eac7","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"4ea3b7ac0a","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"直荷，即柳直荷（1898-1932），湖南长沙人，毛泽东早年的战友。1924年加入中国共产党，1932年9月在湖北洪湖革命根据地被害。"},{"id":"a84e7105cd","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"4ea3b7ac0a","index":5,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"柳午亭（1877—1957），湖南长沙人，柳直荷的父亲。"}],"contents":[{"id":"525c09589d","type":"title","text":"给李淑-的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"4ea3b7ac0a"},{"id":"8d94599eea","type":"paragraph","text":"淑一同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"4ea3b7ac0a"},{"id":"d3e07b588a","type":"paragraph","text":"惠书收到。过于谦让了。我们是一辈的人，不是前辈后辈关系，你所取的态度不适当，要改。已指出“峡”，读者已知所指何处，似不必再出现“三峡”字面。大作读毕，感概系之。开慧所述那一首不好，不要写了吧。有《游仙》一首为赠。这种游仙作者自己不在内，别于古之游仙诗。但词里有之，如咏七夕之类。我失骄杨君失柳，杨柳轻随直上重会九。问讯吴刚何所有，吴刚摔出桂花酒。寂簧嫩舒广袖，万里长空且为思魂舞。忽报人间曾伏虎，泪飞顿作倾盆雨","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"4ea3b7ac0a"},{"id":"7d5d96f41e","type":"paragraph","text":"暑假或寒假你如有可能，请到板仓代我看一看开慧的墓。此外，你如去看直有的基的时候，请为我代致掉意。你如见到柳午亭先生时，请为我代致问候。午亭先生和你有何困难，请告。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"4ea3b7ac0a"},{"id":"b20145eac7","type":"paragraph","text":"为国珍摄！","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"4ea3b7ac0a"},{"id":"a84e7105cd","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"4ea3b7ac0a"},{"id":"37efe081e0","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五七年五月十一日","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"4ea3b7ac0a"}],"page":{"id":"610481fb6f","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"4ea3b7ac0a","start":72,"end":73}},"wenji7":{"comments":[{"id":"0c1751b0df","publicationId":"wenji7","articleId":"4ea3b7ac0a","index":4,"part_index":3,"offset":34,"text":"直荀，即柳直荀（一八九八——一九三二），湖南长沙人，毛泽东早年的战友。一九二四年加入中国共产党，一九三二年九月在湖北洪湖革命根据地被害。"},{"id":"320fd5ad01","publicationId":"wenji7","articleId":"4ea3b7ac0a","index":5,"part_index":3,"offset":55,"text":"柳午亭（一八七七——一九五七），湖南长沙人，柳直荀的父亲。"},{"id":"8c1f13427f","publicationId":"wenji7","articleId":"4ea3b7ac0a","index":2,"part_index":2,"offset":83,"text":"开慧，即杨开慧（一九○一——一九三○），湖南长沙人，毛泽东的夫人。一九二一年加入中国共产党，一九三○年十月被国民党反动派逮捕，十一月牺牲。"},{"id":"be64449a37","publicationId":"wenji7","articleId":"4ea3b7ac0a","index":1,"part_index":0,"offset":4,"text":"李淑一（一九○一——一九九七），湖南长沙人，柳直荀的夫人。当时是湖南长沙第十中学语文教员。"},{"id":"c9cffe0191","publicationId":"wenji7","articleId":"4ea3b7ac0a","index":3,"part_index":2,"offset":88,"text":"指《虞美人·枕上》（《毛泽东诗词集》，中央文献出版社1996年版，第166页）。"}],"contents":[{"id":"0c1751b0df","type":"paragraph","text":"为国珍摄！","index":4,"publicationId":"wenji7","articleId":"4ea3b7ac0a"},{"id":"2fdcc49035","type":"paragraph","text":"根据人民出版社一九八三年出版的","index":7,"publicationId":"wenji7","articleId":"4ea3b7ac0a"},{"id":"3100491b90","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五七年五月十一日","index":6,"publicationId":"wenji7","articleId":"4ea3b7ac0a"},{"id":"320fd5ad01","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":5,"publicationId":"wenji7","articleId":"4ea3b7ac0a"},{"id":"3ec8b5c43b","type":"title","text":"给李淑一的信","index":0,"publicationId":"wenji7","articleId":"4ea3b7ac0a"},{"id":"7f8a10ef3d","type":"paragraph","text":"《毛泽东书信选集》刊印。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenji7","articleId":"4ea3b7ac0a"},{"id":"8c1f13427f","type":"paragraph","text":"惠书收到。过于谦让了。我们是一辈的人，不是前辈后辈关系，你所取的态度不适当，要改。已指出“巫峡”，读者已知所指何处，似不必再出现“三峡”字面。大作读毕，感慨系之。开慧所述那一首不好，不要写了吧。有《游仙》一首为赠。这种游仙，作者自己不在内，别于古之游仙诗。但词里有之，如咏七夕之类。我失骄杨君失柳，杨柳轻飏直上重霄九。问讯吴刚何所有，吴刚捧出桂花酒。寂寞嫦娥舒广袖，万里长空且为忠魂舞。忽报人间曾伏虎，泪飞顿作倾盆雨。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenji7","articleId":"4ea3b7ac0a"},{"id":"be64449a37","type":"appellation","text":"淑一同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenji7","articleId":"4ea3b7ac0a"},{"id":"c9cffe0191","type":"paragraph","text":"暑假或寒假你如有可能，请到板仓代我看一看开慧的墓。此外，你如去看直荀的墓的时候，请为我代致悼意。你如见到柳午亭先生时，请为我代致问候。午亭先生和你有何困难，请告。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenji7","articleId":"4ea3b7ac0a"}],"page":{"id":"9344d30019","publicationId":"wenji7","articleId":"4ea3b7ac0a","start":307,"end":307}}}},"__N_SSG":true}